channel.title: Simple Fix? [Delta]
channel.description:
Hey,
Just got the following errors in NPCHandler while compiling the server:
[CODE]NPCHandler.java:3053: illegal start of expression public boolean ResetAttackNPC(int NPCID) { ^ NPCHandler.java:3053: ';' expected public boolean ResetAttackNPC(int NPCID) { ^ NPCHandler.java:3053: ';' expected public boolean ResetAttackNPC(int NPCID) { ^ NPCHandler.java:3067: illegal start of expression public boolean ResetAttackPlayer(int NPCID) { ^ NPCHandler.java:3067: ';' expected public boolean ResetAttackPlayer(int NPCID) { ^ NPCHandler.java:3067: ';' expected public boolean ResetAttackPlayer(int NPCID) { ^ NPCHandler.java:3079: reached end of file while parsing }→ ^ 7 errors Finished! Wrong.
If you look closely at his error, you’ll see the error prints:
Exception in thread “main” java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "1264 "

Remove the space wherever the string is.[/quote]
